The Pot Shots series is back with its 4th edition looking at another
seductive selection of progressive, minimal and electronic trance boppers for
your dancing pleasure. In our biggest instalment yet, the 10 tracks provide
for a mixture of styles by established and upcoming artists all intent to
showcase grooving beats and sonic sounds. With a style of its own bouncing and
weaving its way from hypnotic trance to dance floor bouncers, Pot Shots iv is
a dish best served loud for your dancing shoes.
